# Spinner Demo - 12 animated loading indicators
Source demos/settings.tape
Output demos/gifs/spinner.gif

Hide
Type "cargo run --example spinner_demo"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show

# Watch all spinners animate
Sleep 3s

# Navigate through spinners
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms
Down
Sleep 500ms

# Pause all
Space
Sleep 1s

# Resume
Space
Sleep 2s

# Navigate more
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms
Down
Sleep 400ms

Sleep 2s

Type "q"
